---
layout: base.njk
title: Privacy
permalink: /privacy/index.html
---
<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-24 relative">
  <!-- Decorative Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-container rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-30 animate-blob"></div>
  <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-tertiary-container rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-30 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>

  <div class="relative bg-surface-container-low p-10 md:p-14 rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-outline-variant/10 scrapbook-rotate-1">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
      <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-fixed rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-fixed shadow-md -rotate-3">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">shield_person</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary">{{ privacySettings.page_title | default("Privacy & Trust") }}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed font-body">
      {% if privacySettings.body %}
      {{ privacySettings.body | markdownToHtml | safe }}
      {% else %}
      <p class="font-medium text-primary-dim">Your creative journey is safe with us. We believe in total transparency about how our website works.</p>
      
      <div class="bg-surface-container-highest p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-tertiary">
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-tertiary mb-2">1. Secure Messaging (Formsubmit)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm">When you send an inquiry, join a community, or request a bulk order, your messages are securely routed directly to our inbox via <strong>Formsubmit.co</strong>. We do not sell or store this data on a public database—it goes straight to our team to help you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-surface-container-highest p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-secondary">
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-secondary mb-2">2. Your Shopping Cart (Local Storage)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm">We don't use creepy tracking cookies to follow you across the internet. Instead, your shopping cart is saved securely and locally on <strong>your own device</strong> using Browser LocalStorage. Your cart belongs to you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-surface-container-highest p-6 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-primary">
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-2">3. Payments & Live Chat (Tawk.to)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm">We process orders manually via GCash to ensure a personal touch. We will <strong>never</strong> ask for your GCash MPIN on this site. You can chat with us live using <strong>Tawk.to</strong>, which provides our secure on-site chat experience.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm opacity-60 italic mt-8 border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-6">Update this page with your shop's official legal policy inside the CMS at <strong>/admin</strong> → Privacy Settings.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes blob {
    0% { transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1); }
    33% { transform: translate(30px, -50px) scale(1.1); }
    66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.9); }
    100% { transform: translate(0px, 0px) scale(1); }
  }
  .animate-blob {
    animation: blob 7s infinite;
  }
  .animation-delay-2000 {
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }
</style>
